e a director attached to it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSister Rosetta Tharpe was \u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-2018-nina-simone-leads-new-class-of-inductees/\"\u003einducted\u003c/a\u003e into \u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/tags/rock-hall/\"\u003ethe Rock \u0026amp; Roll Hall of Fame\u003c/a\u003e in 2018. At the induction ceremony, Alabama Shakes’ Brittany Howard led \u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/brittany-howard-performs-sister-rosetta-tharpe-tribute-at-rock-hall-induction-watch/\"\u003ea musical tribute\u003c/a\u003e to Tharpe. The musician was portrayed in the Baz Luhrmann film \u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/thepitch/elvis-movie-review-baz-luhrmann/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eElvis\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e by Yola.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLizzo’s first major dramatic film role came in 2019’s \u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/cardi-b-and-lizzo-appear-in-new-film-hustlers-first-trailer-watch/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eHustlers\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e. The musician has been returning to the spotlight in the wake of \u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/lizzo-responds-to-harassment-lawsuit-too-outrageous-not-to-be-addressed/\"\u003elegal battles\u003c/a\u003e with \u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/lizzo-no-longer-facing-harassment-lawsuit-from-former-tour-employee/\"\u003eformer employees\u003c/a\u003e. She’s got two new singles—“\u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/watch-lizzo-video-for-new-song-love-in-real-life/\"\u003eLove in Real Life\u003c/a\u003e” and “\u003ca href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/listen-to-lizzo-new-song-still-bad/\"\u003eStill Bad\u003c/a\u003e”—and plans to release a new album soon. Plus, she will be performing on \u003ca data-offer-url=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DHY-SLJuIwl/\" data-event-click=\"{\u0026#34;element\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ExternalLink\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;outgoingURL\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https://www.instagram.com/p/DHY-SLJuIwl/\u0026#34;}\" hre